description: The EDULIS project (2016-2018) aims to investigate the economic and ecological feasibility of mussel farming in offshore wind farms and analyses the forces acting on a mussel longline. A life cycle analysis and a business case will be developed to examine the economic feasibility of offshore mussel farming.
keywords: maricultuur, mariculture, edulis, cpower, Agricultural and aquaculture facilities
name: EDULIS mariculture project (C-Power, Belgian part of North Sea, 2016-2018)
